    "ogDescription": "",
    "ogImage": ""
  },
  "pageTitle": "Send your waste stream and project conditions",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"contact-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">Project Inquiry</p>\n        <h1 id=\"contact-title\">Send your waste stream and project conditions</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">For a more useful recommendation, share your waste type, target capacity, site limits, destination country, and the product direction you are considering. That gives WEI LAN enough context to start the engineering discussion properly.</p>\n        <div class=\"page-chip-row\" aria-label=\"Project information highlights\">\n          <span>Waste Type</span>\n          <span>Capacity Target</span>\n          <span>Site Area</span>\n          <span>Output Goal</span>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"contact-section\" aria-labelledby=\"form-title\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Project Brief</p>\n          <h2 id=\"form-title\">Engineering review is organized around waste stream, capacity, site, and output data</h2>\n          <p>After receiving your project details, the engineering team can review the waste stream, capacity target, site conditions, and automation expectations, then recommend a suitable system configuration path.</p>\n          <div class=\"process-list\" aria-label=\"Next-step workflow\">\n            <span>Engineering review process</span>\n            <span>Configuration recommendation</span>\n            <span>Technical review</span>\n            <span>Commercial review</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <form class=\"contact-form\" data-contact-form action=\"/api/contact\" method=\"post\">\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            Name\n            <input name=\"name\" autocomplete=\"name\" required>\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            Email\n            <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" autocomplete=\"email\" required>\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            Company\n            <input name=\"company\" autocomplete=\"organization\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            WhatsApp / Phone\n            <input name=\"phone\" autocomplete=\"tel\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-narrow\">\n            Country / Region\n            <input name=\"country\" autocomplete=\"country-name\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-narrow\">\n            Target Capacity\n            <input name=\"capacity\" placeholder=\"Example: 2 t/h or 100 t/h\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-narrow\">\n            Available Site Area\n            <input name=\"siteArea\" placeholder=\"Plant footprint or layout limits\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-full\">\n            Product Interest\n            <span class=\"product-interest-picker\" data-product-picker>\n              <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"product\" data-product-value required>\n              <button class=\"product-interest-control\" type=\"button\" data-product-control aria-haspopup=\"listbox\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                <span data-product-label>Choose product line</span>\n                <span class=\"product-interest-chevron\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              </button>\n              <span class=\"product-interest-menu\" data-product-menu role=\"listbox\" aria-label=\"Product interest\">\n                <button class=\"product-interest-option\" type=\"button\" data-product-option=\"AI optical sorting center\" role=\"option\">AI optical sorting center</button>\n                <button class=\"product-interest-option\" type=\"button\" data-product-option=\"Construction and bulky waste recycling line\" role=\"option\">Construction and bulky waste recycling line</button>\n                <button class=\"product-interest-option\" type=\"button\" data-product-option=\"Both systems\" role=\"option\">Both systems</button>\n              </span>\n            </span>\n          </label>\n          <div class=\"form-field form-field-full waste-type-field\" data-waste-type-field>\n            <span class=\"field-label\" id=\"waste-type-label\">Waste Type</span>\n            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wasteType\" data-waste-type-value>\n            <div class=\"waste-type-picker\" data-waste-picker>\n              <button class=\"waste-type-control is-placeholder\" type=\"button\" data-waste-control aria-labelledby=\"waste-type-label\" aria-haspopup=\"listbox\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-disabled=\"true\" disabled>\n                <span data-waste-label>Select product line first</span>\n                <span class=\"waste-type-chevron\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              </button>\n              <div class=\"waste-type-menu\" data-waste-menu>\n                <div class=\"waste-type-options\" data-waste-options role=\"listbox\" aria-label=\"Waste type suggestions\"></div>\n                <div class=\"waste-type-create-row\">\n                  <input data-waste-custom autocomplete=\"off\" placeholder=\"Type custom waste type\">\n                  <button class=\"waste-type-custom-clear\" type=\"button\" data-waste-custom-clear aria-label=\"Clear custom waste type\">&times;</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"waste-type-menu-actions\">\n                  <button class=\"waste-type-clear\" type=\"button\" data-waste-clear>All</button>\n                  <button class=\"waste-type-done\" type=\"button\" data-waste-done>Done</button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-full\">\n            Project Details\n            <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" placeholder=\"Material composition, output target, voltage, automation requirements, timeline\" required></textarea>\n          </label>\n          <div class=\"form-submit-row\">\n            <p class=\"contact-note\">Sales hotline: +86 137 8001 2268 / +86 180 6737 7770</p>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Request Engineering Proposal</button>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"form-status\" data-contact-status role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\"></p>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section service-section\" aria-labelledby=\"next-steps-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Next Steps</p>\n          <h2 id=\"next-steps-title\">Inquiry handling moves from project data to configuration recommendation</h2>\n          <p>Most projects do not need a long discovery phase at the start. A clear first RFQ is usually enough to move into practical technical review.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-grid\">\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">01</span>\n            <h3>Project data intake</h3>\n            <p>Send the waste type, target capacity, and plant limits so the team can understand the operating context.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">02</span>\n            <h3>Engineering review process</h3>\n            <p>WEI LAN reviews material type, likely process modules, and the overall project direction before discussing configuration.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">03</span>\n            <h3>Configuration recommendation</h3>\n            <p>The team recommends the most suitable product line, process path, and configuration range for deeper evaluation.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">04</span>\n            <h3>Technical and commercial review</h3>\n            <p>Once the basic fit is clear, the conversation can move into documents, parameters, and commercial discussion.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section dark-section\" aria-labelledby=\"checklist-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ Inputs</p>\n          <h2 id=\"checklist-title\">Engineering review improves when core operating inputs are complete</h2>\n          <p>Even a short first message becomes much more actionable when it includes the operational basics below.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-grid\">\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">Input 01</span>\n            <h3>Material composition basis</h3>\n            <p>Clarify whether the material is PET, HDPE, PP, mixed plastics, construction waste, decoration waste, or bulky waste.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">Input 02</span>\n            <h3>Capacity basis</h3>\n            <p>Share the expected hourly throughput so the recommendation can stay inside the right model and module range.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">Input 03</span>\n            <h3>Site constraint basis</h3>\n            <p>Available footprint, layout restrictions, voltage, and local operating limits all affect solution direction.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">Input 04</span>\n            <h3>Output target basis</h3>\n            <p>Explain the recycled products, purity goals, or final material direction you want the system to support.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"cta-band\" aria-labelledby=\"rfq-support-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">Project Preparation</p>\n        <h2 id=\"rfq-support-title\">Inquiry planning moves faster with product data, solution paths, and technical files</h2>\n        <p>If your team is still comparing options, use the supporting pages to narrow the project direction, then return with the most relevant waste stream and capacity target.</p>\n        <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/products\">Explore Product Lines</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">Review Resources</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
